{"tid":2117190,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"山西金融辦主任落馬 傳家中查出4億現金","createTime":"2020-07-20T15:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T04:40:53.000Z","uid":53062,"like":85,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"5233603ee02418fa8498f833d37bfa0b29e7f68c","tid":2117190,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T15:58:46.000Z","msg":"7月19日晚，山西省紀委監委通報，山西省地方金融監督管理局（省政府金融辦）原黨組書記、局長（主任）竟暉涉嫌嚴重違紀違法，目前正接受調查。<br />\n<br />\n法制晚報記者微信公眾號「觀海內參」引述消息人士透露，竟暉的案子有點大，6月初被免職時就已經出事了，家裡被發現藏了4個億的現金。這一數字超過了國家能源局煤炭司副司長魏鵬遠和中國華融公司前董事長賴小民。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wyG5VAF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwyG5VAF.jpg&h=68aa4831&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/7/20/n12270240.htm/amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F7%2F20%2Fn12270240.htm%2Famp&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP8tNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=cf331315\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/7/20/n12270240.htm/amp</a>"},{"pid":"92673ba9ecc2b31fd868c69c2948841d67d6a9a9","tid":2117190,"uid":53062,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T16:00:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20200720/35816332.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.news.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20200720%2F35816332.html&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP8tNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=de896251\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20200720/35816332.html</a><br />\n<br />\n山西金融系統接連打虎。<br />\n<br />\n據中央紀委國家監委駐中國銀保監會紀檢監察組、山西省紀委監委7月20日發佈消息：原中國銀監會山西監管局黨委書記、局長張安順涉嫌嚴重違紀違法，目前正接受紀律審查和監察調查。"},{"pid":"176f8d1d84742509ef7417a968ff81b57c59334d","tid":2117190,"uid":3775,"like":87,"dislike":0,"score":87,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T16:02:18.000Z","msg":"嗯嗯 <br />\n4億算得乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e5d5dd9d0bea6174741800ffaefd9e0f4e394c5","t